                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18500916-1671-offence-1 t18500916-name-592"></join>William M'Lellan</persName>, and stealing 1 handkerchief, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; his goods.</rs>
