                        <interp inst="t18500916-name-594" type="given" value="FRANCIS"></interp>FRANCIS IRELAND</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, L</hi> 119). I took the prisoner into custody, on 19th Aug., and found this handkerchief in his coat pocket—I asked him where he got it—he said he bought it about eighteen months ago, over the water.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I bought it in Petticoat-lane.</p>
